      <title>Announcement</title>
      <link>https://rustycruiselabs.github.io/home/announcement/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://rustycruiselabs.github.io/home/announcement/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;a-hyper-casual-color-matching-game-youll-love&#34; class=&#34;headerLink&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#a-hyper-casual-color-matching-game-youll-love&#34; class=&#34;header-mark&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;A Hyper Casual Color-Matching Game You’ll Love!&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is our second shot at releasing a mobile game — and it’s been a blast bringing our game jam idea to life! Weirdly enough, it turned out to be pretty satisfying to play! You can find more details about the game &lt;a href=&#34;games/blob-bridge&#34; rel=&#34;&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;! Blob Bridge is now available on &lt;a href=&#34;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rustycruiselabs.blobbridge&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;Google Play&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blob-bridge/id6748570064&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;App Store&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
